snippet: Stan Wawrinka's stunning defeat of top-ranked Novak Djokovic in the U.S. Open final on Sunday booked the Swiss his place at the ATP World Tour Finals in London at the end of the year....
lead_paragraph: Stan Wawrinka's stunning defeat of top-ranked Novak Djokovic in the U.S. Open final on Sunday booked the Swiss his place at the ATP World Tour Finals in London at the end of the year.

headline.print_headline: Wawrinka Seals Spot in ATP World Tour Finals
headline.main: Wawrinka Seals Spot in ATP World Tour Finals
